chart_description: This chart shows the duration in milliseconds for which some memory pressure has been applied to the system and the processes have been stalled waiting for access to memory. This can help diagnose memory-related performance issues.

dimension_descriptions.some 10: This dimension shows the 10-second moving average of the stall time.
dimension_descriptions.some 300: This dimension shows the 5-minute moving average of the stall time.
dimension_descriptions.some 60: This dimension shows the 1-minute moving average of the stall time.
